            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "You can accurately recall anything you have seen or heard within the past month."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "html": "<div id=\"page-content\">\n<p>Source: Player's Handbook</p>\n<p>You have a mind that can track time, direction, and detail with uncanny precision. You gain the following benefits.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>You always know which way is north.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>You always know the number of hours left before the next sunrise or sunset.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>You can accurately recall anything you have seen or heard within the past month.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"
